1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
What if I told you AI doesn’t think, it predicts?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:09,200
Large language models, like transformers, work with tokens—think of them as puzzle pieces.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:15,600
They use attention mechanisms to focus on relevant pieces, predicting the next token based on context.

4
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:19,600
But here's the catch: they can hallucinate, generating false information.

5
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:23,200
So while they're powerful, they don’t 'understand'—they just predict.

6
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,600
Want to learn more about AI?

7
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,400
Hit that follow button and stay curious!
